abstract: ASSOCIATIONS OF WILD HORSES. -- Life in societies is again the rule with the large family of horses, which includes the wild horses and donkeys of Asia, the zebras, the mustangs, the cimarrones of the Pampas, and the half-wild horses of Mongolia and Siberia. The storm raged with great severity for nearly seven hours, and over half a foot of snow fell.

abstract: ST. LOUIS, Mo., Jan. 30. -- The contents of a mail box were found yesterday in Holmes  Co.'s lumber yard, at Tenth and Spruce Streets, and Superintendent Dice and his railway inspectors are trying to solve the mystery of the robbery, for there is no doubt that a robbery, and a pretty big one, has been committed.
